=== Decision rule: TL vs MLP h=64 P@2 across data sizes ===
  n=  50  TL= 88.7%  MLP h=64= 89.8%  gap=-1.1pp  → MLP wins
  n= 200  TL= 87.7%  MLP h=64= 91.7%  gap=-4.0pp  → MLP wins
  n= 500  TL= 88.0%  MLP h=64= 91.1%  gap=-3.1pp  → MLP wins
  n=2000  TL= 88.0%  MLP h=64= 91.3%  gap=-3.3pp  → MLP wins

=== Decision rule: TL vs MLP h=64 in-occluder recall across data sizes ===
  n=  50  TL= 95.5%  MLP h=64= 91.1%  gap=+4.4pp  → TL wins
  n= 200  TL= 97.5%  MLP h=64= 93.3%  gap=+4.2pp  → TL wins
  n= 500  TL= 98.2%  MLP h=64= 97.5%  gap=+0.7pp  → near-tie
  n=2000  TL= 97.9%  MLP h=64= 99.9%  gap=-2.0pp  → MLP wins
